description:
In this episode of Star Players, Grammy award-winning DJ Zedd takes us through his gaming journey from Alex Kidd, to fostering his love of rock music through Gran Turismo. Oh, and we make him play DJ Hero.

Zedd joins host Lucy James to go over his lifelong love of games, from developing a passion for competitive shooters starting with Counter Strike: Source, to touring with four PS4s to play Overwatch anywhere with anyone.
title: We Made Zedd Play DJ Hero For The First Time | Star Players

description: Get an in-depth look at Shattered Space in this deep dive with Bethesda Game Studios. Uncover the many mysteries surrounding House Va’ruun and explore an isolated, handcrafted new world in Starfield’s first major story expansion.
title: Starfield: Shattered Space - Official Deep Dive Gameplay Trailer
